# Charts Examples in Zolt

## Basic Chart Container

Simple chart with one graph:

:::chart
:::chart-line {title="Sales Over Time"}
Jan: 100
Feb: 120
Mar: 150
Apr: 180
:::
:::
:::

## Multiple Charts in Container

Several graphs sharing the same space:

:::chart
:::chart-line {title="Revenue"}
2020: 50000
2021: 75000
2022: 100000
2023: 125000
:::

:::chart-bar {title="Expenses"}
2020: 30000
2021: 35000
2022: 40000
2023: 45000
:::
:::
:::

