Feb: 20
Mar: 30
:::

:::chart-line {color-scheme=warm title="Warm Colors"}
Jan: 10
Feb: 20
Mar: 30
:::
:::
:::

### Chart with Legend

:::chart
:::chart-bar {title="Sales by Region" legend=true}
North: 450
South: 320
East: 280
West: 390
:::
:::
:::

### Chart with Grid

:::chart
:::chart-line {title="Detailed View" grid=true}
Jan: 100
Feb: 150
Mar: 200
:::
:::
:::

## Practical Examples

### Financial Report

```yaml
---
title: "Q4 Financial Report"
date: 2026-02-18
---
```

